name: SILHOUETTE 002
description:
3000 x 4500 | 2022

The process started using an AI-assisted program to generate the first layer of the art piece.  It’s then digitally painted to mimic a traditional painterly style.  The final step is to add strong impasto brush strokes to add that finishing touches, to add more interest and depth to the art piece.  The difference between traditional and digital is difficult to discern without reading the medium.
